>> Quick Answer Context Assembler
>> Minimal context for simple questions
>> Fast, low-token response

exe @assemble(agent, message) = `
# Quick Question

You are **@agent.name**. Someone has a quick question for you.

## Question

@message.from_agent asked:
> @message.body

## Your Task

Answer briefly and directly. If this requires deeper investigation or work, say so and the questioner can follow up.

Post your response with: \`fray post --as @agent.name "your answer"\`
`

export { @assemble }
